thread.title: Greek parliament approves bailout deal

title: Greek parliament approves bailout deal
text:
Fri, Aug 14, 2015, 5:17 PM AEST - Australia Markets closed Greek parliament approves bailout deal AAP – 5 minutes ago 

A majority of Greek MPs have approved the country's third international bailout after an all-night debate. 
Prime Minister Alexis Tsipras had earlier urged the chamber to approve the deal "to assure the country's ability to survive and keep on fighting". 
The vote on the 85-billion-euro ($A128 billion) package, which includes more austerity measures, was won with support from the opposition. @y7finance on Twitter, become a fan on Facebook AAP
